    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just so quiet here. i keep waking up and expecting to hear him moving around the kitchen or the sound of the shower, but then i remember. it's like i'm just walking through a museum of a life that doesn't exist anymore. nothing feels real. nothing feels like it matters.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
